Matches include: Jake “The Snake” Roberts vs Ravishing Rick Rude ⦁ Intercontinental Championship Match  Ultimate Warrior (c) vs. Honky Tonk Man  ⦁  Hulk Hogan vs King Haku ⦁ Hart Foundation vs Fabulous Rougeau Brothers ⦁ Mr. Perfect vs Jumping Jim Brunzell ⦁ Koko B. Ware vs Big Boss Man ⦁ Blue Blazer vs Jose Estrada ⦁ Paul Roma vs Steve Lombardi
